Comment: 0,0:00:33.47,0:00:33.47,OPJP,,0,0,0,,OPJP
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.43,0:00:42.48,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}Pink blood, pink blood, pink blood
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.85,0:00:46.48,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}誰にも見せなくても
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.48,0:00:50.07,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}キレイなものはキレイ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.07,0:00:52.49,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}もう知ってるから
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.49,0:00:56.08,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}誰にも聞かなくても
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.08,0:00:59.66,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}キレイなものはキレイ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.66,0:01:03.08,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}もう言ってるから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.08,0:01:07.92,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}あなたの部屋に歩きながら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.92,0:01:12.63,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}床に何個も落ちる涙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.63,0:01:17.47,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}自分の価値もわからないような
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.47,0:01:22.31,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}コドモのままじゃいられないわ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.31,0:01:27.11,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}心の穴を埋める何か
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.11,0:01:31.82,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}失うことを恐れないわ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.82,0:01:36.70,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}自分のことを癒せるのは
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.70,0:01:41.08,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}自分だけだと気付いたから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.08,0:01:45.92,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}サイコロ振って出た数進め
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.92,0:01:50.71,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}終わりの見えない道だって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.71,0:01:55.26,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}王座になんて座ってらんねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.26,0:02:00.89,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}自分で選んだ椅子じゃなきゃダメ
Comment: 0,0:00:28.92,0:00:28.92,OPCN,,0,0,0,,OPCN
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.85,0:00:46.48,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}就算谁都不曾见过
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.48,0:00:50.07,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}美丽的东西就是美丽的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.07,0:00:52.49,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}我早已知晓
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.49,0:00:56.08,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}就算谁都不曾听闻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.08,0:00:59.66,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}美丽的东西就是美丽的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.66,0:01:03.08,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}我早已言说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.08,0:01:07.92,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}一步步走向你的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.92,0:01:12.63,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}一滴滴落在地板的泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.63,0:01:17.47,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}我不愿继续做那个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.47,0:01:22.31,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}不知自爱的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.31,0:01:27.11,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}我不再害怕失去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.11,0:01:31.82,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}那些填补内心空洞的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.82,0:01:36.70,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}因为我已经发现
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.70,0:01:41.08,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}人只能自己治愈自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.08,0:01:45.92,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}扔出骰子 按点数向前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.92,0:01:50.71,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}就算前路漫漫 看不到头
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.71,0:01:55.26,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}哪怕王座 也不能阻挡我的脚步
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.26,0:02:00.89,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}我要坐上 自己选的那张椅子
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,EDJP,,0,0,0,,EDJP
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,EDCN,,0,0,0,,EDCN
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Title
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.98,0:02:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord1\fs120\fsp15\fnFOT-Lyra Std DB\c&H020103&\3c&H00013A&\pos(970,740)}不死之身的死
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.01,0:24:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord1\fs100\fsp15\fnFOT-Lyra Std DB\c&H020103&\3c&H00013A&\pos(970,740)}然后走向日出
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,screen,,0,0,0,,screen
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Dialogue
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.65,0:00:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,战斗开始后4天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.36,0:00:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,王都连利尔陷入了空前的混乱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.03,0:00:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,杀人犯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.70,0:00:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,敌人的进攻不知何时才会停止
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.37,0:00:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不死被逼到了绝境
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.91,0:00:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不灭的三战士亦是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.59,0:00:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我想解脱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.71,0:00:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.72,0:00:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我会保护你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.98,0:02:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,住手 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.74,0:02:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,别杀小不
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.07,0:02:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.66,0:02:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,难道你是…玛琦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.87,0:03:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,快停下 左手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.74,0:03:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,再不赶快停下…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.50,0:03:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.41,0:03:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.37,0:03:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,都怪我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.66,0:03:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,全部…都被它们夺走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.80,0:03:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,终于…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.18,0:03:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我还以为…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.76,0:04:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,终于能见面了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.47,0:04:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,多少年
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.77,0:04:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我花了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.73,0:04:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,多少年
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.32,0:04:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你总是马上又消失不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.24,0:04:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,又丢下了玛琦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.63,0:04:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,伤口…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.55,0:04:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.31,0:04:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.14,0:04:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 我不能消沉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.85,0:04:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.19,0:04:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.48,0:04:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我能行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.65,0:04:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我要去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.40,0:04:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,玛琦要去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.28,0:05:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.87,0:05:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,当然是要去救小不
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.62,0:05:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么救
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.67,0:05:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你在这待着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.04,0:05:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我去叫医生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.17,0:05:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧 马儿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.63,0:05:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.55,0:05:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,城市停止运转了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.68,0:05:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,损坏的房子没有修复
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.69,0:05:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,弹药也没有补充
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.15,0:05:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,就像完全失去了抵抗一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.73,0:05:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你又昏过去了吗 不死
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.65,0:05:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不 同样的失误他应该不会犯两次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.90,0:05:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,难道说 他死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.91,0:05:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不死
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.45,0:05:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你才没有死 小不
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.30,0:06:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.34,0:06:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,出什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.43,0:06:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,守卫被干掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.60,0:06:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,敲门者…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.90,0:06:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,手上闲着的人 来帮我们做障碍物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.36,0:06:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,要快点好起来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.99,0:06:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,尤伊丝妈妈 我先过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.25,0:06:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,卡姆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.54,0:06:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你见到一个叫米盖尔的民兵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.71,0:06:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,能帮我转告他尤伊丝在这里等他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.96,0:06:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,米盖尔？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.59,0:06:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,是男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.06,0:06:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,包在我身上吧 阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.81,0:06:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我一定把他带来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.44,0:07:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,在不死复活之前坚持住
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.16,0:07:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,那才那匹马 是不是有个女孩骑在上面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.12,0:07:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,马儿 看那里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.96,0:07:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,有人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.04,0:07:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是增援吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.52,0:07:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.44,0:07:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我是玛琦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.69,0:07:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐 医生在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.40,0:07:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,在这 这是医院
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.32,0:07:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.32,0:07:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我家里有个伤员
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.20,0:07:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,快去小不家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.11,0:07:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,小不？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.20,0:07:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,就是不死
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.41,0:07:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了 我会带人过去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.74,0:07:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你快从后面走 去避难
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.16,0:07:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,糟了 箭用光了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.46,0:08:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,塞拉 用这个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.88,0:08:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 米盖尔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.51,0:08:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你背后露给敌人了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.06,0:08:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.93,0:08:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,快到里面处理一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.31,0:08:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,可以从后门进去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.90,0:08:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不 先搞定这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.48,0:08:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,从这里往城堡那边走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.28,0:08:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不死的同伴应该就在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.99,0:08:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 大姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.21,0:08:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不死没有反应
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.59,0:08:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,梅沙尔 你在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.26,0:08:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,凯 海洛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.60,0:08:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,王子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.01,0:08:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,哪里都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.81,0:08:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,连利尔太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.73,0:09:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,从天上找呢 至少能找到不死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.10,0:09:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我们恐高啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.69,0:09:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我找到了凯的尸体
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.28,0:09:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,看样子 是被迦白干掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.36,0:09:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,迦白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.50,0:09:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你在那里吗 不死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.80,0:09:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.67,0:09:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你一个人在这干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.47,0:09:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你爸爸在附近吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.51,0:09:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,一直以来谢谢您照顾不死 彭叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.73,0:09:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.15,0:09:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,200年前被当作祭品的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.74,0:10:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我们一起去小不那里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.50,0:10:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道他在哪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.46,0:10:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不死 你在家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.01,0:10:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 大哥哥不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.56,0:10:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,他已经被医生带走了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.23,0:10:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,这里发生什么了 玛琦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.98,0:10:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不死他就像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.78,0:10:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,然后整个身子被扭成了一团
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.20,0:10:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,被那个矢野目的大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.70,0:10:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,被迦白…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.71,0:10:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,都怪我 把不死一个人留在这
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.21,0:10:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,小不他有努力试着回来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.84,0:10:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,但是没能成功
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.88,0:10:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥想砍断自己的手臂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.30,0:10:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,结果有一个圆滚滚的东西从手臂里跑出来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.68,0:11:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不知跑哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.93,0:11:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不死就是在这消失的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.06,0:11:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,叔叔 他真的不在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.86,0:11:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,小不没跟你说「我在这」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.57,0:11:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,就像当初你找到我们的时候那样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.32,0:11:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你找不到小不吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.21,0:11:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 他不在这
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.09,0:11:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我没看到他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.01,0:11:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我看不到他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.10,0:11:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,到此为止了吗 不死
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.15,0:11:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我们…就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.48,0:11:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,快跑 这里已经撑不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.61,0:11:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,快看 城里已经无处可逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.95,0:12:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 一点也没减少
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.62,0:12:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,撑住 塞拉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.71,0:12:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,要是我们倒下了 医院里的人就没救了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.59,0:12:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我们 就要这么…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.92,0:12:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,完蛋了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.88,0:12:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是你想看到的吗 黑先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.39,0:12:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,看着不死和连利尔一起完蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.35,0:12:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你满意了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.48,0:12:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,这有什么不好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.11,0:12:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.53,0:12:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,非常不好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.12,0:12:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以夺走生命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.20,0:12:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,无论如何也不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.08,0:12:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,那再夺回来就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.34,0:12:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,喵咪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.42,0:13:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.76,0:13:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.12,0:13:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.17,0:13:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,小不
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.79,0:13:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是小不吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.26,0:13:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,绳子还连着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.72,0:13:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是说不死还和城市连着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.14,0:13:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.43,0:13:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你最后的挣扎吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.23,0:13:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,如果能让你再次拥有意识
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.15,0:14:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们试试吧 叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.86,0:14:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,要让小不变回人类
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.11,0:14:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,把失去的都夺回来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.12,0:14:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,但是办不到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.33,0:14:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,敲门者的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.91,0:14:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,只有同样让敲门者寄生的迦白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.33,0:14:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,或者说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.12,0:14:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,被敲门者当作异物夺走的不死才知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.13,0:14:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,凭我们没办法找到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.96,0:14:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们就不停地找
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.96,0:14:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,玛琦会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.93,0:14:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,它们在看着我们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.01,0:14:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不会让我们轻易找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.85,0:14:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,敲门者那么聪明
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.52,0:14:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定会藏在我们永远也找不到的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.19,0:14:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就只能眼睁睁看着连利尔死去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.61,0:14:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,一方是无限增殖的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.53,0:14:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,另一方是死去便无法复活的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.66,0:14:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.71,0:14:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,小不
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.04,0:14:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,真的没有办法了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.34,0:15:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我们该怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.97,0:15:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的想不起大家了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.50,0:15:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,米盖尔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.46,0:15:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,这里交给我 你快带塞拉去医院
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.67,0:15:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我还能战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.71,0:15:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,快去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.46,0:15:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.72,0:15:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.63,0:15:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,对 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.97,0:15:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不死不光是被夺走了外形
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.68,0:15:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,记忆里那个人对应的样子也被夺走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.77,0:15:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,外貌和声音
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.23,0:16:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那个黑叔叔说过外貌 声音 和气味被夺走了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.24,0:16:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,是这样吗 黑先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.54,0:16:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,外貌 声音 气味
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.66,0:16:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,如果告诉他这些 他就能想起大家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.92,0:16:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,但要怎么告诉他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.88,0:16:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,对这个看不见也听不见的不死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.80,0:16:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,要怎样让它产生变化呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.51,0:16:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我们能给它什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.90,0:16:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.23,0:16:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,卡姆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.11,0:16:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 快走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.07,0:16:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不 放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.61,0:16:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我得去救他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.74,0:16:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,快走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.16,0:17:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,玛琦 你能去外面等一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.38,0:17:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,然后开始数数
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.21,0:17:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你数到100我还没有出来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.71,0:17:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,就骑上马 去奇力亚特地区的乌拉里斯军营
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.34,0:17:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,把这个拿给他们看 他们就会帮助你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.35,0:17:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.15,0:17:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,话说 喵咪去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.49,0:17:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,得赶快
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.70,0:17:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,玛琦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.16,0:17:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你叫我来的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.91,0:17:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在终于理解了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.54,0:17:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不死
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.09,0:17:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,卡姆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.01,0:17:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不要 快起来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.14,0:18:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.86,0:18:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,全都给我想起来 不死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.06,0:18:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是我的梦境吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.73,0:18:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,真让人愉悦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.59,0:19:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,王子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.71,0:19:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不死 快醒醒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.08,0:19:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\bord0.5}我…我是这里的佣人 叫谷谷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.71,0:19:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\bord0.5}你叫什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.96,0:19:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\bord0.5}我叫托娜莉 请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.63,0:19:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\bord0.5}好了 不死
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.26,0:19:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\bord0.5}咱们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.34,0:20:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\bord0.5}别傻站着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.76,0:20:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.94,0:20:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,睁开眼睛 不死
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.70,0:20:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.53,0:20:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.02,0:20:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.94,0:20:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,成功了 我们得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.48,0:20:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,神还没有抛弃我们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.65,0:21:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,伤员都来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.82,0:21:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧 塞拉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.12,0:21:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.71,0:21:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,卡姆 我要救卡姆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.50,0:21:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,卡姆他…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.59,0:21:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,卡姆他喜欢尤伊丝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.38,0:21:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,他肯定知道你将来会和尤伊丝成家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.22,0:21:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,所以才这么拼命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.19,0:21:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要带着卡姆的份一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.52,0:21:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,保护城里的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.86,0:21:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我们能做到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.32,0:21:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,当然能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.34,0:22:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,快进去 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.21,0:22:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,塞拉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.46,0:22:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不会 让你 逃 走 的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.95,0:24:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不死回到了最初的形态
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.08,0:24:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,得知了一切的彭
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.67,0:24:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,为不死赌上了自己的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.92,0:24:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,还有一线希望
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.13,0:24:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,为了和敲门者做个了断
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.47,0:24:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不死之身的伙伴们纷纷站了起来
